app_detail:
A simple and colorful earthquake app that focuses in the synthesis of earthquakes provided by national and international data agencies for an easy and updated vision.

Features:
• Simple, elegant design;
• Interactive map and globe view;
• Complete/Personalized and up-to-date list of earthquakes*;
• Event search by date, keyword and distance;
• Closest cites to epicenter (available for some events on USGS);
• Shape of tectonic plates;
• Event details;
• Earthquake notifications with full control on location, distance and magnitude;
• Tsunami notifications;
• Built-in seismograph;
• Real-time statistics;
• Real-time felt reports, comments and global chat;
• No ads;

*The list of earthquakes uses a fusion technology that allows to view only distinct events from the enabled providers and have control over the merging strategy.
